  "content": "<div class=\"content-main relative\">\n <h1 class=\"block text-[4rem] text-[var(--dark)] leading-[4.4rem] font-semibold mb-[5px]\">Nhanh ch&oacute;ng ứng cứu người d&acirc;n bị v&ugrave;i lấp do sạt lở đất</h1>\n <div class=\"content-meta flex items-center flex-wrap flex-row text-[1.3rem] leading-[2rem] font-normal text-[#999] truncate h-[30px] mb-[10px] [&amp;&gt;:not(:first-child)]:ml-[25px]\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n   <a href=\"/bao-tin-tuc-ttxvn-tin-tuc-ttxvn-p294.epi\" class=\"bm-card-source flex items-center shrink-0\" title=\"B&aacute;o Tin Tức TTXVN\">\n    <figure class=\"image opacity-80 w-auto h-[16px]\" style=\"width:45px;height:20px\" aria-label=\"Logo nh&agrave; xuất bản\">\n     <picture>\n      <source srcset=\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/bb071048550abc54e51b.png\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n      <source srcset=\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/bb071048550abc54e51b.png\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n      <img src=\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/bb071048550abc54e51b.png\" alt=\"B&aacute;o Tin Tức TTXVN\" width=\"144\" height=\"64\" />\n     </picture>\n    </figure></a>\n   <span><button class=\"relative text-[14px] leading-[normal] font-normal text-center cursor-pointer normal-case border-0 transition-button disabled:shadow-none disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed follow-button flex items-center item-star ml-[10px]\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" title=\"Theo d&otilde;i &quot;Tin Tức TTXVN&quot;\" aria-label=\"Button\"><i class=\"icon inline-block font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-star text-[var(--primary)]\"></i></button></span>\n  </div>\n  <time datetime=\"2025-11-02T11:59:00.000Z\">7 giờ trước</time>\n  <a href=\"/cong-an-xa-phuoc-thanh-t41578286.epi\" class=\"related inline !text-[#adb5bd] hover:!text-[var(--primary)]\">11\n   <!-- --> li&ecirc;n quan</a>\n  <a href=\"/nhanh-chong-ung-cuu-nguoi-dan-bi-vui-lap-do-sat-lo-dat-r53653354.epi\" class=\"origin item-origin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><i class=\"icon inline-block font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-copy text-[13px] mr-[5px]\"></i><span>Gốc</span></a>\n </div>\n <h3 class=\"sapo block text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] font-semibold text-[var(--dark)] p-[10px] bg-[#f2f4f5]\">Ng&agrave;y 2/11, C&ocirc;ng an x&atilde; Phước Th&agrave;nh, th&agrave;nh phố Đ&agrave; Nẵng cho biết, v&agrave;o khoảng 14 giờ ng&agrave;y 2/11, tại th&ocirc;n 4, x&atilde; đ&atilde; xảy vụ sạt lở đất l&agrave;m v&ugrave;i lấp 6 căn nh&agrave; v&agrave; 1 người d&acirc;n.</h3>\n <div class=\"content-body text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] text-black mt-[15px] break-words overflow-hidden [&amp;_h1]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_h2]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_h3]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_h4]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_h5]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_p]:mb-[15px] [&amp;&gt;div]:mb-[15px]\">\n  <p class=\"text\">Ngay khi nhận tin b&aacute;o, C&ocirc;ng an x&atilde; Phước Th&agrave;nh đ&atilde; khẩn trương phối hợp Ban Chỉ huy Ph&ograve;ng thủ <a class=\"tag-link\" href=\"/hinh-su-dan-su.epi\">d&acirc;n sự</a> x&atilde; triển khai lực lượng, phương tiện tổ chức cứu nạn, cứu hộ. Đến khoảng 15 giờ 30 ph&uacute;t, lực lượng đ&atilde; cứu được nạn nh&acirc;n ra ngo&agrave;i v&agrave; đưa đến Trung t&acirc;m Y tế x&atilde; cấp cứu, nạn nh&acirc;n chỉ bị thương nhẹ.</p>\n  <p class=\"text\">Hiện C&ocirc;ng an x&atilde; Phước Th&agrave;nh tiếp tục vận động, hỗ trợ di dời 20 hộ d&acirc;n với 60 nh&acirc;n khẩu đến nơi an to&agrave;n, căng d&acirc;y cảnh b&aacute;o khu vực nguy hiểm, bảo đảm <a class=\"tag-link\" href=\"/an-ninh-trat-tu.epi\">an ninh trật tự</a>, an to&agrave;n cho nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n.</p>\n  <p class=\"text body-author text-right\"><strong>Trần Tĩnh (TTXVN)</strong></p>\n </div>\n <div class=\"pswp\" tabindex=\"-1\" role=\"dialog\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n  <div class=\"pswp__bg\"></div>\n  <div class=\"pswp__scroll-wrap\">\n   <div class=\"pswp__container\">\n    <div class=\"pswp__item\"></div>\n    <div class=\"pswp__item\"></div>\n    <div class=\"pswp__item\"></div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"pswp__ui pswp__ui--hidden\">\n    <div class=\"pswp__top-bar\">\n     <div class=\"pswp__counter\"></div>\n     <button type=\"button\" class=\"pswp__button pswp__button--close\" title=\"Close (Esc)\"></button>\n     <button type=\"button\" class=\"pswp__button pswp__button--share\" title=\"Share\"></button>\n     <button type=\"button\" class=\"pswp__button pswp__button--fs\" title=\"Toggle fullscreen\"></button>\n     <button type=\"button\" class=\"pswp__button pswp__button--zoom\" title=\"Zoom in/out\"></button>\n     <div class=\"pswp__preloader\">\n      <div class=\"pswp__preloader__icn\">\n       <div class=\"pswp__preloader__cut\">\n        <div class=\"pswp__preloader__donut\"></div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"pswp__share-modal pswp__share-modal--hidden pswp__single-tap\">\n     <div class=\"pswp__share-tooltip\"></div>\n    </div>\n    <button type=\"button\" class=\"pswp__button pswp__button--arrow--left\" title=\"Previous (arrow left)\"></button>\n    <button type=\"button\" class=\"pswp__button pswp__button--arrow--right\" title=\"Next (arrow right)\"></button>\n    <div class=\"pswp__caption\">\n     <div class=\"pswp__caption__center\"></div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"content-social absolute top-[55px] w-[40px] h-full ml-[-75px]\">\n  <div class=\"content-social-container relative top-[unset] bottom-[unset] text-center w-[50px]\">\n   <button class=\"btn-social btn-facebook w-[40px] h-[40px] flex items-center justify-center text-[20px] mt-0 mb-[10px] rounded-[50%] bg-[#4e598f] hover:bg-[#3c446e]\" title=\"Chia sẻ qua Facebook\"><i class=\"bm-icon inline-block bg-[url(https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/bm-icon-2.0.3.png)] bg-[length:100px_4250px] align-middle w-[40px] h-[40px]